## The Pattern (Applied Everywhere)
```
predict → apply → observe → confirm → supersede if wrong
```
- Tile lifecycle: Active → Superseded → Retracted
- Lamport clocks for causal ordering
- PLATO v3 integration: /submit, /supersede, /stats
- ~95% PLATO write reduction when predictions confirm

